(79, 'widget_text', 'a:4:{i:1;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:4:"Text";s:4:"text";s:124:"Distinctively utilize long-term high-impact total linkage whereas high-payoff experiences. Appropriately communicate 24/365.";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:2;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:25:"About teaching for tutors";s:4:"text";s:460:"<p>Welcome to Teaching to Freedom. I am a teacher and have always had a keen interest in the areas of money and finance. I have always held a dream to have saved enough money to be able to retire early or to earn enough passive income so that I can do the things in life that I most enjoy.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top:25px">[mks_button size="small" title="Find out more" style="squared" url="/about-us" target="_blank" bg_color="#f44336" txt_color="#FFFFFF"]</p>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:3;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:12:"About Author";s:4:"text";s:425:"<p><img src="http://localhost:8888/teaching/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/unnamed-2-e1484656166721.jpg" alt=""></p>\r\n<p>Hi, I’m Damien, I am a secondary school teacher aiming for financial independence. I have accumulated a great wealth of knowledge over the years and would now like to share my journey and hopefully inspire others to realise that a mediocre paid job is not the end of the road to financial independence.</p>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;}', 'yes'),
